net.powermatcher.api.data

Class PointBid

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.powermatcher.api.data.Bid
      • net.powermatcher.api.data.PointBid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<PricePoint>

    public class PointBid
extends Bid
implements java.lang.Iterable<PricePoint>
    This immutable data object represents a Bid with a PricePoint array to represent the bid curve. This is used by Agents that have to create a Bid, because it is easier to create.
